videos.description: Syracuse's Frank Howard gets the ball in transition and finishes the finger roll in the first half.
videos.headline: Howard converts fast break finger roll

videos.description: After grabbing the steal on defense, Notre Dame's Rex Pflueger goes in transition and throws down the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Pflueger turns defense into offense

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyus Battle kicks the ball out to Oshae Brissett for the 3-point shot to beat the buzzer in the second half.
videos.headline: Brissett beats the shot clock with 3-ball

videos.description: Notre Dame's TJ Gibbs finds John Mooney down low for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Gibbs finds Mooney inside for the two-handed slam

videos.description: Syracuse's Oshae Brissett dishes the ball to Tyus Battle behind the arc for the tough 3-point shot in the second half.
videos.headline: Battle sinks contested 3-pointer

videos.description: Syracuse's Marek Dolezaj tries finishing the two-handed dunk but is rejected by Notre Dame's Elijah Burns.
videos.headline: Burns denies Dolezaj in the paint

videos.description: Notre Dame's Martinas Geben hauls in the offensive rebound and sinks the tough layup late in the second half.
videos.headline: Geben converts huge second-chance points
